🟪 Card Components
Use #111111 background


Rounded corners: 12px


Padding: 16px internal


Apply shadow only subtly (optional): dark-mode friendly shadows like shadowColor: '#000', shadowOpacity: 0.3, shadowRadius: 8



🌗 Dark Mode Considerations
All components designed natively for dark mode


Avoid pure white contrast blocks; keep everything slightly muted


Use gradients of the accent color subtly in progress bars, active tab indicator, etc.



🧭 Iconography
Monoline icons (outline style)


Prefer Lucide, Feather, or Phosphor for lightweight, modern icons


All icons should inherit the current text color unless overridden